Feature: A new video can be added if a proper properties are given
    
    Scenario: creation is successful with valid properties
     	Given command "a" add new readtip is selected and command "1" video is selected
        When  Author "Author" and Title "title" and Link "wwww" and Description "desc" and Year published "2000" are input
        Then  a new videotip is added

Feature: A new book can be added if a proper properties are given

	Scenario: creation is successful with valid properties
     	Given command "a" add new readtip is selected and command "2" book is selected
        When  Author "Author" and Title "title" and ISBN "12345" and Description "desc" and Year "2000" are input
        Then  a new booktip is added


